{"title":"炸村庄","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":15,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5676","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>xw建造了一个村庄，村庄为一个m*n的正方形，每一格都有一个房子,生命值为a[m][n],如果amn为0，这里就没有房子。现在lt想要炸掉xw的村庄，但他想尽可能用较少的TNT，一个TNT可以对3*3的范围造成1点伤害，请问lt最少用几个TNT可以炸了这个村庄？</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>两个数m和n</p><p>接下来把这个村庄每个生命值输出来</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个数，lt需要最少TNT个数</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4 4</p><p>0 2 2 2</p><p>2 4 3 2</p><p>2 3 4 2</p><p>2 2 2 0</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1&lt;=m,n&lt;=100</p><p>数据比较水</p><p><br></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}